## pypic config
the file should look like this:

[distutils] 
index-servers=conti


[conti]
####repo for internal users
#repository: https://artifactory.8675.ccp.continental.exchange/artifactory/api/pypi/caedge-generic-simulation
####repo for external users or cloud 9
repository: https://artifactory-tls.8675.ccp.continental.exchange/artifactory/api/pypi/caedge-generic-simulation
